weren’t born in Ireland, if you had an acceptable link, lucky you, Irish citizenship was yours.

00:02:31.252 --> 00:02:36.642
On the other side of the world, however, there are people who are not quite so lucky, as they

00:02:36.642 --> 00:02:42.232
live in a country that is not quite so accommodating when it comes to handing out citizenship.

00:02:42.932 --> 00:02:49.602
In Kuwait, there are people who might never have left the country, whose parents, grandparents, and

